  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Just as a Brahmin actor does not forget his being a Brahmin, whatever part
he may be acting, so also a man should not confound himself with his body,
but he should have a firm awareness of his being the Self, whatever his
activity may be.
